                "editor": "<p style='font-size: 15px; color: #5B6470;'>Have a complex technology problem? Want to transition your factory to solar, automate your company's CRM workflow, or install a secure biometric smart network in your home? Reach out directly to our Founder & Chief Consultant Sanjeev Goel.</p>"
